{"tid":1020150,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)鐵血戰士+S 異手指1-2","createTime":"2019-02-13T12:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T20:29:32.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0479c1542353e2e3d9dd7b420b1e6987a05b48d5","tid":1020150,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=81b2ecf5\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=178da16c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=7ab6baf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/puirhoe/1449156956-204164012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fpuirhoe%2F1449156956-204164012.jpg&h=77c41624&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://cfile21.uf.tistory.com/image/99A424335A07059B33EBAF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile21.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F99A424335A07059B33EBAF&h=2d7ff686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.艾倫&middot;薛弗是美國特種部隊小組長，奉命率隊前往中美洲叢林執行秘密救援任務並蒐集情報。在任務完成時，他們俘虜了一名女性，隨後啟程向集合地點前進。途中遭遇不明敵人侵襲，小組成員接連被殺，僅剩艾倫與女戰俘兩人。<br />\n艾倫在跌落泥水池後，終於發現對手是身著可隱形盔甲的外星戰士，而且無法「看到」全身沾滿泥漿的自己。艾倫利用地形地物布置陷阱，歷經許多艱險後，終於殲滅對手..<br />\n<br />\n2.影片的主角是一個叫做羅伊斯的僱傭兵，他被奇異的外星怪物－－&ldquo;掠奪者&rdquo;（Predator）綁架，並被甩到了掠奪者的星球上。和他一起在這個星球上和&ldquo;掠奪者&rdquo;一起廝殺的還有7個戰士與一個外科醫生。這些人都是從地球上各個角落挑選出..<br />\n<br />\n3.2004年，一顆人造衛星在南極洲以北約1600公里的布韋島地下檢測到一個神秘的熱源。億萬富翁，跨國通訊公司韋蘭德實業的老闆查爾斯&middot;比夏普&middot;韋蘭德集結了一隊科學家前往該地進行調查。這些人中包括考古學家、語言學專家、鑽井工人、僱傭兵和一位叫亞歷克薩&middot;伍茲的嚮導..<br />\n<br />\n4.劇情緊接著第一集，一個終極戰士被異形植入卵，因而產生了一個超強的終極異形，而堪稱電影史最兇殘兩大外星生物「異形」（Alien）和「終極戰士」（Predator） ，再度在地球上全盤引爆世紀聖戰家園！人類不幸淪為兩派異獸的獵物，通通被捲入「異形」和「終極戰士」之間冷血的戰火中，該如何自救？<br />\n<br />\n8 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=6463a1f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=d25adb44\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9224a5999886052da985c3aec898e1a9f6387c30","tid":1020150,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T12:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71586b337db9223cd1b55189b4287a3f41ba6807","tid":1020150,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s